<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
	<head>
		<title>The Setup / <%= @this.type == :post ? @this.name : @this.title %></title>
		<link href="/stylesheets/screen.css" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
		<link href="/feed/" rel="alternate" title="Atom feed" type="application/atom+xml">
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
		<% if @this.type == :post %>
		<meta property="og:title" content="<%= @this.name %>" />
		<meta property="og:description" content="<%= @this.summary %>" />
		<meta property="og:url" content="http://<%= @this.slug %>.usesthis.com/" />
		<meta property="og:type" content="article" />
		<meta property="og:image" content="http://usesthis.com/images/portraits/<%= @this.slug %>.jpg" />
		<meta property="og:image:width" content="500" />
		<meta property="og:image:height" content="335" />
		<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
		<meta name="twitter:site" content="@usesthis">
		<meta name="twitter:creator" content="@waferbaby">
		<% else %>
		<meta property="og:title" content="The Setup<% if @this.title %><%= " / #{@this.title}" %><% end %>" />
		<meta property="og:description" content="What do people use to get stuff done?" />
		<meta property="og:url" content="http://www.usesthis.com/" />
		<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
		<% end %>
		<script src="http://stats.usesthis.com/?js" type="text/javascript"></script>
		<base href="http://usesthis.com/">
	</head>
	<body>
		<div id="wrapper">
			<div id="stump">
				<header>
					<% if @this.type == :post %><a href="/" title="The most recent interviews."><% end %>
					<h1>The Setup</h1>
					<h2><% if @this.type == :post %>Interview<% else %><%= @this.title %><% end %></h2>
					<% if @this.type == :post %></a><% end %>
					<p id="tagline">What do people use to get stuff done?</p>
				</header>

				<nav id="main">
					<ul>
						<li><a href="/" title="The most recent interviews.">Home</a></li>
						<li><a href="/interviews/" title="All the other interviews.">Interviews</a></li>
						<li><a href="/community/" title="Other interviews by people like you.">Community</a></li>
						<li><a href="/about/" title="A little more info about the site.">About</a></li>
					</ul>

					<p id="feeds">Follow along on <a href="http://twitter.com/usesthis/" title="The @usesthis Twitter account.">Twitter</a>,
					or subscribe to the <a href="/feed/" title="Subscribe to the Atom feed.">feed</a>.</p>
				</nav>

				<div id="sellout">
					<script type="text/javascript">
					//<![CDATA[
					(function(id) {
					 document.write('<script type="text/javascript" src="' +
					   'http://connect.decknetwork.net/deck' + id + '_js.php?' +
					   (new Date().getTime()) + '"></' + 'script>');
					})("SU");
					//]]>
					</script>
					<p><em>Ads Via <a href="http://decknetwork.net/" title="The Deck ad network.">The Deck</a></em></p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div id="content">
			<%= yield %>
			</div>

			<footer>
				<p>This is a <a href="http://twitter.com/waferbaby" title="Some dork's Twitter account.">waferbaby</a> snafu, published every <strong>Tuesday</strong> and <strong>Thursday</strong> (last updated <%= Time.now.strftime('%b %d, %Y') %>). Unless otherwise noted, everything is available via the <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/" title="A Creative Commons license.">Attribution-Share Alike</a> license.</p>
				<p>Hosting provided by <a href=" https://www.digitalocean.com/?refcode=b59c4de92bdc" title="My lovely hosting provider (with a referral code in the link)." rel="nofollow">DigitalOcean</a>.</p>
				<p>You're awesome.</p>
			</footer>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>